<Prose
  title="Privacy Policy: welanutria"
  description="How welanutria handles data, cookies and advertising."
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  updated="June 2026"
>
  <p>This policy explains how welanutria ("we", "us") handles information when you use welanutria.com. We keep things minimal: the site has no accounts and asks for no personal details to work.</p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p><strong>Calculator inputs.</strong> The values you type into our calculators (such as age, height or weight) are processed in your browser to produce a result. We do not require an account and we do not store these inputs on our servers.</p>
  <p><strong>Usage data.</strong> Like most websites, we may collect standard, non-identifying analytics, such as which pages are visited and general device or browser type, to understand how the site is used and improve it.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We may use cookies and similar technologies for basic site functionality, analytics, and advertising. You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling some cookies may affect how parts of the site work.</p>

  <h2>Advertising &amp; affiliate links</h2>
  <p>welanutria is supported by advertising and affiliate links. Third-party advertising partners may use cookies to show relevant ads and measure their performance; these partners operate under their own privacy policies. Affiliate links mean we may earn a commission if you buy something through them, at no extra cost to you.</p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>We rely on third-party providers to host and run the site (for example, our hosting provider and font and analytics services). These providers process limited technical data needed to deliver the site.</p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You can use most of the site without accepting non-essential cookies.</li>
    <li>You can clear or block cookies in your browser at any time.</li>
    <li>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access or request deletion of data held about you. Contact us to ask.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>welanutria is intended for a general adult audience and is not directed at children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "last updated" date above reflects the latest version.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:hello@welanutria.com">hello@welanutria.com</a>.</p>

  <p class="note">This policy is provided for general information and is not legal advice. For obligations specific to your jurisdiction, consult a qualified professional.</p>
</Prose>
